title: Assets under supervision at Goldman Sachs 2009 to 2018
yAxis: Assets under supervision in billion U.S. dollars
summary: In general Assets under supervision in billion U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Assets under supervision in billion U.S. dollars is slightly increasing from 2012 to 2016, and lastly roughly constant from 2016 to 2018.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2013 and 2014.
Maximum Assets under supervision in billion U.S. dollars, about 1542.0 was reported at Year 2018
The lowest Assets under supervision in billion U.S. dollars, of value 965.0 was reported at Year 2012
